<li>#13504, #13625, +<a href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml/issues/14223=
">#14223</a>: Add <code>Thread.set_current_thread_name</code>.
(Romain Beauxis, review by Gabriel Scherer and Antonin D=C3=A9cimo)</li>

<li><a href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml/issues/13541">#13541</a>, <a =
href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml/issues/13777">#13777</a>: Using C++1=
1 <code>thread_local</code> causes name-mangling
issues when linking with flexlink on Cygwin.
(Antonin D=C3=A9cimo and David Allsopp, report by Kate Deplaix)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</li>
<li><a id=3D"org1f28563"></a>Runtime fixes<br />
<div class=3D"outline-text-5" id=3D"text-org1f28563">
