href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml/issues/14221">#14221</a>: fix a conf=
used error message for module inclusions,
functor error messages were missing some type equalities potentially leading
to nonsensical "type t is not compatible with type t" submessage
(Florian Angeletti, report by Basile Cl=C3=A9ment, review by Gabriel Schere=
r)</li>
